| 1 | [specific task — not "work on thesis"] | Stage N | 2 | todo / in-progress / done / blocked | YYYY-MM-DD |
| 2 | [specific task] | Stage N | 1.5 | todo | YYYY-MM-DD |
| 3 | [specific task] | Stage N | 1 | todo | YYYY-MM-DD |
| 4 | — | — | — | — | — |
| 5 | — | — | — | — | — |

