## Daily Standup History (Rolling 7 Days)

> Yesterday / Today / Blockers format. Appended by 12_daily-standup.md.

### [YYYY-MM-DD]
- Yesterday: [what was done or "rest day"]
- Today: [what was planned]
- Blockers: [list or "none"]
- Energy: [N/5]

### [YYYY-MM-DD — previous day]
- Yesterday: ...
- Today: ...
- Blockers: ...
- Energy: ...

